  "texts": [
    "We used the inconsistency to help refine the prompt instead of adjusting the model's hyperparameter.",
    "Through trial and error, we developed a more detailed prompt that delivered more consistent fine-grained results from the model with the baseline model parameters (see Prompt #4).",
    "In two different chats, we gave each of these prompts to ChatGPT for all the documents.",
    "With the more specific prompt, the results showed more consistency across documents in terms of the form of the model's response, but there was also some loss in the richness compared to the best responses with the more open prompt because the second prompt led",
    "ChatGPT to focus on formulating a good answer to each of the questions instead of best representing the text."
